[1.019686, "o", "  MultiKueue evaluates GPU capacity across all worker clusters\r\n  and dispatches each job to a cluster with available resources.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[2mClusters: us-east1 (8 GPUs) + us-west3 (8 GPUs) = 16 GPUs total\u001b[0m\r\n"]
